<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Redirect Notice</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 3em;
            color: #e74c3c;
        }
        h2 {
            font-size: 2em;
            color: #555;
        }
        ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        li {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
    </style>
    {% if redirect_location %}
    <meta http-equiv="refresh" content="5; url={{ redirect_location }}">
    {% endif %}
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Redirect {{ status_code }}</h1>
    <h2>Notice: Resource has moved.</h2>
    <p>The resource you are looking for has moved or requires further action. Here are the details:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Status Code:</strong> {{ status_code }} - {{ status }}: {{ description }}</li>
    </ul>

{% if reasons %}
    <p>Additional information include:</p>
    <ul>
        {% for reason in reasons %}
            <li>Error {{ reason.status_code }}: {{ reason.message }}</li>
        {% endfor %}
    </ul>
    {% else %}
    <p>No additional reasons were provided for this status.</p>
{% endif %}
    {% if redirect_location %}
    <p>You will be redirected to the new location shortly. If the redirection does not occur, please <a href="{{ redirect_location }}">click here</a>.</p>
    {% else %}
    <p>Unfortunately, the new location of this resource is not available at this time.</p>
    <p>Please check back later, or contact support if you believe this to be an error.</p>
    {% endif %}
</body>
</html>